(509, 1, '2015-09-02 16:47:45', '2015-09-02 16:47:45', 'What the heck is the Lotto Rainbow?\r\n\r\nThe lotto rainbow is just another very helpful mathematical tool to help you <strong>Play Smart and Win More.</strong> I did not create the Lotto Rainbow, it has been around for years and used successfully by many lotto pros. Yes, there are professional lottery players. Didn''t you know that?\r\n<blockquote><em>A new study, arguing that not all combinations of numbers have the same probability, suggests there could be an art to predicting the winning numbers. You will learn that winning a lottery is not merely a matter of luck: by having the right information you will be able to create game strategies. We will show you how to play in a very simple and easy way, based on the fact that drawings are subordinated to a behavior pattern</em></blockquote>\r\nFirst, the Lotto Rainbow tool divides up numbers by colors.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/hoosierlotteryhelper/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/rainbow.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-479" src="http://localhost/hoosierlotteryhelper/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/rainbow.png" alt="" width="538" height="225" /></a>\r\n\r\nEven if you pick very different numbers in two games, for example, it might have the same color template.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/hoosierlotteryhelper/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/rainbow_pics.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-480" src="http://localhost/hoosierlotteryhelper/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/rainbow_pics.png" alt="" width="555" height="116" /></a>\r\n\r\nFrom there, the tool describes different types of color template combinations.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/hoosierlotteryhelper/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/rainbow_stats.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-481" src="http://localhost/hoosierlotteryhelper/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/rainbow_stats.png" alt="" width="584" height="202" /></a>\r\n\r\nNow what does all this do? Are you confused? Want to really learn how to win the lotto then you should take advantage of our free membership and go through lotto training. Our basic and advanced memberships are a sure bet to winning more in the lotto. You get access to all the Hoosier Lotto stats and a lotto prediction program that uses these and other tools to give you the most probabilistic balls that will be drawn next. We help you <strong>Play Smart and Win More</strong>.\r\n\r\nAlthough there are other variations, here is the most logical rainbow table to play the Hoosier lottery.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/hoosierlotteryhelper/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/rainbow_table.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-508" src="http://localhost/hoosierlotteryhelper/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/rainbow_table.png" alt="" width="1250" height="571" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'The Lotto Rainbow', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '468-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-02 16:47:45', '2015-09-02 16:47:45', '', 468, 'http://localhost/hoosierlotteryhelper/2015/09/02/468-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
