(578, 1, '2015-09-07 02:43:52', '2015-09-07 02:43:52', 'So what the heck is a Lottery Wheel?\r\n<blockquote><b>Lottery wheeling</b> (also known as <b>lottery</b> system, <b>lottery wheel</b>, <b>lottery wheeling</b> system) is an entertaining strategy of playing the lotteries, widely used by individual players and syndicates to secure wins provided they hit some of the drawn numbers....<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lottery_wheeling" target="_blank">MORE</a></blockquote>\r\nBasically a lottery wheel creates a permutation matrix. So if you hit a least x numbers from your wheeled numbers you are guaranteed to have a ticket with x numbers on it. So let''s say you pick 8 numbers and wheel them. During the drawing 4 of your wheeled numbers were picked, so if you played your entire wheel you have at least one ticket with 4 winners, several with 3 winners, and even more with 2 winners. This is a very good strategy when picking your lotto numbers, and yes as a member there is a very easy to use tool that will make your lotto wheel according to your selected numbers and give you the results.\r\n\r\n<strong>Let''s consider the previous drawing of 9/5/15</strong>\r\n\r\nHere is the simplest raw data available to free members\r\n<blockquote>TopDog Set: 6\r\n[15, 25, 28, 31, 43, 46]\r\nLowDog Set: 25\r\n[2, 4, 5, 6, 10, 11, 12, 13, 18, 19, 20, 21, 23, 24, 32, 33, 34, 35, 36, 38, 39, 40, 42, 44, 47]\r\nTotal Prediction Set: 31</blockquote>\r\nSo let''s say you wanted to wheel this data. Your Lotto wheel contains 736281 picks. So if my system has predicted 6/6 winning numbers (which it has over 140 times) then you are guaranteed to have the winning lottery ticket in this lottery wheel. Jackpot is $4 million, lotto wheel cost you $736,281 (all tax deductible) and you''ve made a pretty profit of ~$3.6 million.\r\n\r\nSo need more than just a Lottery Wheel. That''s why we introduce a rainbow table and even more advanced statistics draw from the previous winners. It also helps to find a good lotto pool. That''s actually one of the main goals of this site and a big advantage to an Advanced Membership is premium verified Lottery Pools.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Lottery Wheels', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'lottery-wheels', '', '', '2015-09-06 02:48:32', '2015-09-06 02:48:32', '', 0, 'http://localhost/hoosierlotteryhelper/?p=578', 0, 'post', '', 0),
